The paper also discusses methods for comparing representations in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) tasks. Additionally, the paper's introduction mentions the use of neural networks in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) more broadly. Therefore, these five categories are the most likely candidates for this paper.
